[normal]d SSHD in these type 
[normal]of cases (
[normal]ie
[normal] non-asylum seeking families) and how to liaise better so as to resolve them more quickly.   Attention of the Court of Appeal on issues clearly benefited the UKBA and 
[normal]local authorities
