[normal]R  (VC and K) v Newcastle CC 
[normal] SSHD as interested party (and arguing against Newcastle)
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](2 judge court, very fully considered)
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal][2011] EWHC 2673
[normal]On who is responsible to support failed asylum-seeking families (who are not entitled to s95 because they became failed asylum-seekers 
[normal]prior
[normal] to the birth of a child) with outstanding applications – 
[normal]local authorities
[normal] under CA s17 or the UKBA under IAA s4?  
[normal] Established that it is s17.   CA s122(5) prevents 
[normal]local authorities 
[normal]providing assistance to children if they would be entitled to s95 support. There is no similar provision regarding s4.
