[normal]his hearing (
[normal]ie
[normal] that she should be
[normal] supported under the CA), K had
[normal] previously applied for s4 support, been 
[normal]refused and lost her appeal to the FTT(AS). So she and her 2 children under 3 would have been totally without support had she not been able to JR Newc
[normal]astle’s unlawful decision
