[normal]SL v Westminster CC 
[normal]Mind and Freedom from Torture as interveners
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal][2013] UKSC 27
[normal]On the meaning of
[normal] the NAA s21 ‘care and attention’ and when a vulnerable asylum-seeker becomes the responsibility of a 
[normal]local authority 
